h may indirectly address anti-black racism.&#10;3. Hon. Bill Blair, as Minister of Public Safety, commits to ensuring all federal agencies under his purview provide training on culturally competent and bias-free delivery of service and creating a diverse workforce that reflects and respects the diverse people of this country. This commitment may help address systemic racism within law enforcement agencies, but it does not directly respond to ending racial profiling or over-policing of black bodies as specifically requested by Mr. Jagmeet Singh.">
