as-free delivery of service and creating a diverse workforce that reflects and respects the diverse people of this country.&#10;&#10;Note: The commitments mentioned above are in response to Mr. Matthew Green's requests, but they were made by various cabinet ministers other than Hon. Patty Hajdu. It is not explicitly stated whether she is willing to make any further commitments regarding anti-black racism beyond her commitment related to ALS.">
